article.headline: Pride puts up 19 as Saint Bonaventure takes down UMass 79-73
article.description: — Charles Pride had 19 points in Saint Bonaventure's 79-73 victory over UMass on Wednesday night.
article.linkText: Pride puts up 19 as Saint Bonaventure takes down UMass 79-73
article.story: OLEAN, N.Y. -- — Charles Pride had 19 points in Saint Bonaventure's 79-73 victory over UMass on Wednesday night. Pride shot 8 of 11 from the field and 3 for 5 from the line for the Bonnies (14-8, 5-5 Atlantic 10 Conference). Chad Venning scored 15 points and added seven rebounds and four blocks. Mika Adams-Woods shot 5 for 9, including 3 for 4 from beyond the arc to finish with 15 points. Matt Cross finished with 19 points, six rebounds and five assists for the Minutemen (14-8, 5-5). Keon Thompson added 16 points and seven rebounds for UMass. In addition, Jayden Ndjigue had 12 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
